<A>__{aft down the side of the ship.}
<L>__{145 in his stateroom, surrounded by piles of plans while making notes in}
<A>__{his ever present book, andrews looks up at the sound of a cut crystal light fixture tinkling like a windchime. he feels the shudder run through the ship. and we see it in his face. too much of his soul is in this great ship for him not to feel its mortal wound.}
